        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3E%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%20text%3D%22%23000000%22%20link%3D%22%230000ff%22%20vlink%3D%22%23800080%22%20bgcolor%3D%22%23feff1f%22%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ccenter%3E%3Ctable%20cellspacing%3D%220%22%20border%3D%220%22%20cellpadding%3D%227%22%20width%3D%22462%22%3E%0A%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20width%3D%2223%25%22%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%0A%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%2272%22%20height%3D%22112%22%3E%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3Ctd%20width%3D%2255%25%22%20valign%3D%22MIDDLE%22%3E%0A%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3EHot%20Peeps%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3Ctd%20width%3D%2222%25%22%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%0A%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%2272%22%20height%3D%22112%22%3E%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIntroduction%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%20It%20is%20common%20knowledge%20that%20Peeps%2C%20while%20abundant%20in%20the%20Spring%2C%20become%20sparse%20by%20early%20summer.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%20Many%20have%20speculated%20that%20this%20dramatic%20population%20reduction%20is%20a%20natural%20result%20of%20complex%20predator%2Fprey%20relationships.%20%20Peep%20populations%20appear%20to%20swell%20up%20until%20the%20bizarre%20convergence%20of%2050%25%20off%20sales%20at%20grocery%20stores%20and%20pharmacies%20around%20the%20world.%20%20Dedicated%20teams%20of%20scientists%2C%20engineers%2C%20and%20astrologists%20have%20yet%20to%20explain%20why%20this%20always%20happens%20on%20a%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EAfter%20extensive%20government-funded%20exploration%20on%20the%20beaches%20of%20Florida%2C%20Maui%2C%20and%20the%20Bahamas%20resulted%20in%20severe%20burns%20to%20our%20research%20team%2C%20we%20learned%20a%20new%20appreciation%20for%20sunblock.%20%20%20Recognizing%20that%20few%20Peeps%20are%20seen%20traveling%20with%20anything%20higher%20than%20SPF4%2C%20we%20began%20to%20suspect%20that%20Peeps%20might%20have%20an%20adverse%20reaction%20to%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMethods%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%20Utilizing%20the%20well-established%20scientific%20axiom%20that%20a%20little%20exposure%20over%20a%20long%20time%20is%20about%20the%20same%20as%20a%20lot%20of%20exposure%20over%20a%20little%20time%20(see%20related%20works%20on%20saccharin%2C%20X-rays%2C%20and%20FD%26amp%3BC%20Red%20number%202)%20%2C%20we%20decided%20that%20the%20best%20tool%20for%20investigating%20heat%20would%20be%20the%20autoclave%20across%20the%20hall.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20an%20autoclave%3F%20%20Imagine%20a%20refrigerator-sized%20pressure%20cooker%2C%20capable%20of%20killing%20any%20living%20tissues%2C%20bacteria%2C%20or%20fungi.%20%20This%20is%20the%20tool%20we%20utilized.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%20Our%20subject%20was%20exposed%20to%2010%20atmospheres%20of%20pressure%20at%20350%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20for%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EResults%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EAs%20suspected%2C%20our%20Peep%20subject%20did%20show%20adverse%20reactions%20to%20the%20experimental%20conditions%2C%20including%2C%20but%20not%20limited%20to%20headaches%2C%20poor%20eyesite%2C%20increased%20density%2C%20and%20general%20gooeyness.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ccenter%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EAs%20shown%20above%20in%20our%20state-of-the-art%20time-lapse%20photography%20sequence%2C%20by%20the%20end%20of%20our%20test%20sequence%20the%20Peep%20has%20returned%20to%20a%20more%20elemental%20state%20known%20commonly%20as%20%22%20Fluff%22%20or%20%22%20Marshmallow%20Fluff%22.%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%5BThe%20photo%20sequence%20will%20repeat%20automatically%20after%20a%20short%20pause%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConclusion%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%20We%20all%20know%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20Venus%20consists%20in%20large%20part%20of%20ammonia.%20%20Early%20unmanned%20Soviet%20exploration%20of%20Venus%20failed%20to%20uncover%20signs%20of%20Peep%20presence%2C%20despite%20all%20speculation%20to%20the%20contrary.%20%20We%20know%2C%20however%2C%20from%20our%20solubility%20tests%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20an%20ammonia%20atmosphere%20alone%20would%20not%20exclude%20feasible%20colonization%20of%20Venus%20by%20ancient%20space-travelling%20Peeps.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%20Furthermore%2C%20observations%20of%20Peep%20biochemistry%20indicate%20a%20molecular%20structure%20unlike%20any%20other%20terrestrial%20organisms%20yet%20encountered%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20obvious%20conclusion%20that%20Peeps%20are%20not%20of%20this%20world%20(Mulder%20%26amp%3B%20Scully%2C%20et.%20al.%201996).%20%20In%20addition%2C%20while%20early%20evolutionary%20biologists%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20variation%20in%20the%20peep%20population%20was%20due%20to%20an%20ancient%20bottleneck%20event%2C%20we%20suggest%20the%20more%20likely%20scenario%20of%20the%20founder%20effect%20phenomenon%20during%20terrestrial%20colonization.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%20Thus%20we%20arrive%20at%20our%20paradigm-shattering%20conclusion%20that%20%20billions%20of%20Peep%20spores%20were%20scattered%20throughout%20the%20galaxy%20millions%20of%20years%20ago%2C%20landing%20on%20all%20planets%20throughout%20our%20solar%20system%20and%20beyond.%20%20While%20these%20courageous%20pioneers%20of%20Peepdom%20fared%20the%20ammonia%20atmosphere%20of%20Venus%20without%20any%20ill%20effects%2C%20the%20temperature%20must%20have%20proved%20to%20much%20for%20even%20the%20heartiest%20marshmallow%20chicks.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22index.html%22%3EReturn%20to%20the%20Peep%20home%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
